# Repair and Warranty Tools
# These tools are defined inline in the agent DSL files.
# This file serves as a tool registry reference for the v2 export format.

# Tools:
#   check_warranty — Check warranty coverage by serial number
#   estimate_repair_cost — Estimate repair cost based on device, issue, and warranty status
#   schedule_in_store_service — Schedule an in-store service appointment at an Apple Store
#   find_nearby_stores — Find nearby Apple Stores with availability
#   get_repair_status — Check the status of an ongoing repair
#   submit_mail_in_repair — Submit a mail-in repair request and get a shipping label
